DataSet<Integer> result = customTypes.map(new MapFunction<CustomType, Integer>() {          private static final long serialVersionUID = -7950126399899584991L.          @Override         public Integer map(CustomType value) throws Exception {             return value.value.         }     }).     result.output(new DiscardingOutputFormat<Integer>()).     env.execute(). }
